This paper deals with the performance of Mobile Ad hoc Networks (MANETs) and the optimization of goodput and delay, which are topics related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also introduces a pricing scheme and analyzes the Nash equilibria of the game, which are topics related to game theory and optimization, making cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) the second likely category. The paper also involves the computation of equilibria and the analysis of the price of anarchy, which are topics related to information theory and optimization, making cs.IT (Information Theory) the third likely category. The paper also involves the study of the effect of pricing on the equilibrium, which is a topic related to control theory, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper involves the study of stochastic geometry, which is a topic related to mathematical analysis, making cs.MA (Mathematical Analysis) the fifth likely category.
